<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

    <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">CBSE Board Preparation</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Courses</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">CBSE</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="course-intro-creative">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="intro-grid">
                <div class="intro-main">
                    <span class="section-tag">Nurture Your Aspirations</span>
                    <h2 class="creative-heading">Cultivating Academic Dreams with <span class="highlight">Agrim
                            Classes</span></h2>
                    <p class="creative-desc">
                        Just as fertile soil nurtures seeds to grow, Agrim Classes is dedicated to cultivating the
                        academic dreams of students, empowering them to excel in the CBSE board exams. With a wide array
                        of specialized programs, we provide students with the resources and guidance needed to thrive in
                        their studies, paving the way for a future filled with opportunities and success.
                    </p>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Your Guide to Excellence</h4>
                        <p>
                            Our mission is to provide each student with the knowledge, skills, and confidence to not
                            only achieve high marks but also develop a deep understanding of subjects. With our support,
                            students are equipped to unlock their full potential and make a positive impact in their
                            chosen fields.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="intro-features">
                    <div class="feature-card-small">
                        <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i></div>
                        <h5>Tailored Coaching Programs</h5>
                        <p>Meticulously crafted to cater to unique needs. Whether it's strengthening core concepts or
                            improving time management, we offer a holistic approach to CBSE preparation.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card-small">
                        <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-road"></i></div>
                        <h5>Embark on Your Journey</h5>
                        <p>Let us nurture your dreams, guide you through the complexities of the CBSE syllabus, and help
                            you achieve a harvest of success in your board exams and beyond.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="boosters-section">
        <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px; padding-top: 60px;">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="main-heading">Exam Preparation Boosters</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="boosters-grid">
                <div class="booster-card card-red">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i></div>
                    <h4>India's Best<br>Ever Team</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-green">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                    <h4>Small Batch Size<br>(Special 20)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                    <h4>Doubt Clearing<br>Session</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="far fa-building"></i></div>
                    <h4>Complete Study Package<br>(Online | Offline)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
                    <h4>Fortnight<br>Test</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="eligibility-section">
        <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
            <h3 class="table-title">CBSE Eligibility Criteria</h3>

            <div class="table-wrapper">
                <table class="eligibility-table cbse-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="th-criteria">Criteria</th>
                            <th class="th-class">Class 10th (Secondary School)</th>
                            <th class="th-class">Class 12th (Senior School Certificate)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Age Limit</td>
                            <td>Minimum 14 years old by 31st March of the examination year</td>
                            <td>Minimum 17 years old by 31st March of the examination year</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Schooling Requirement</td>
                            <td>At least 75% attendance in Class 9 and 10</td>
                            <td>At least 75% attendance in Class 11 and 12</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Subjects</td>
                            <td>Must have passed all subjects in Class 9</td>
                            <td>Must have passed Class 11 and selected a stream (Science, Commerce, Arts)</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Minimum Marks</td>
                            <td>No specific minimum marks required in Class 9</td>
                            <td>Must have passed Class 11 with a minimum of 33% marks</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Private Candidates</td>
                            <td>Not eligible for practical exams</td>
                            <td>Allowed to appear in theory exams but may have limited options for practical exams</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Vocational Subjects</td>
                            <td>Eligible to choose vocational subjects as per CBSE guidelines</td>
                            <td>Eligible to choose vocational subjects based on stream choice</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Subject Selection</td>
                            <td>Must follow the subject combination prescribed by CBSE</td>
                            <td>Subject combination must follow CBSE guidelines for the chosen stream</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Admit Card</td>
                            <td>Must have an admit card issued by the school/CBSE</td>
                            <td>Must have an admit card issued by the school/CBSE</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Practical Exams</td>
                            <td>Must pass both theory and practical exams separately</td>
                            <td>Must pass both theory and practical exams separately</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="course-cta text-center">
                <h3>Ready to Ace your Board Exams?</h3>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Join Agrim Classes Today <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>